Man in Spain in Hospital With E.Coli Symptoms, Cadena Ser Says

-- B y   C h a r l e s   P e n t y
-- 
2011-05-31T06:44:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-31/man-in-spain-in-hospital-with-e-coli-symptoms-cadena-ser-says.html
A 40 year-old man is in hospital in
the Spanish city of San Sebastian with symptoms of the E.coli
infection, Cadena Ser radio station reported on its website.  The man, who has been in hospital for 10 days, is in a
serious condition, the radio station said, without saying where
it got the information. The man had recently been in  Germany ,
Cadena Ser said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
